^5Help - Smail
~5USAGE: .smail ^5user message
~5WHERE: ^5user ~5is an alias
       ^5message ~5is a message you wish them to get

~5Use this command when you want to leave a ^5message to ^5user ~5that can be
~5read later.  This works even if ^5user ~5is offline.  If they are online,
~5they will be notified immediately that you have written them smail.

~5Typing ^5.smail ~5on a line by itself will show you the last 10 smails you
~5sent out.

~5SEE ALSO
  ^5.help rmail~5, ^5.help cmail

